licenseType.content: licenseType → int (Read Only): Returns the license type for this product entry on the dongle.

updateDate.content: updateDate → tuple[int, int, int] (Read Only): The date the product entry is valid until. Returns a tuple in the form (YYYY, MM, DD).

version.content: version → str (Read Only): The version of TouchDesigner this dongle product entry is valid for.
